15
00:00:59.518 --> 00:01:00.643
Ηold on a second.

16
00:01:03.564 --> 00:01:05.356
He's Abu Nazir's
bomb maker, David.

17
00:01:05.441 --> 00:01:08.067
Execute him now,
and everything he knows
is gone forever.

18
00:01:08.152 --> 00:01:09.861
You had your shot.
It's over.

19
00:01:09.945 --> 00:01:12.238
l'm on my way
to the prison now.
At least petition JSOC.

20
00:01:12.364 --> 00:01:14.866
Have them appeal
to the Iraqi army.
JSÓC can't do anything either.

21
00:01:14.950 --> 00:01:17.869
David, you're
a C.l.A. deputy director.
