- l told you it's over.
- Please don't shut me down.

23
00:01:20.497 --> 00:01:22.457
David. Senator Feldman's
looking for you.

24
00:01:22.541 --> 00:01:24.125
Tell him l'll be right there.
David, please.

25
00:01:24.209 --> 00:01:25.918
This is my last chance
with Hasan.

26
00:01:26.003 --> 00:01:28.171
Carrie, l have to go.
I'm hanging up.
David!

27
00:01:28.255 --> 00:01:29.922
[ Line Clicks, Dial Tone ]

28
00:01:34.094 --> 00:01:37.722
