[ Speaking Arabic ]

30
00:01:42.561 --> 00:01:44.771
Estes didn't go for it.

31
00:01:44.855 --> 00:01:47.315
l knew he wouldn't.
I just-

32
00:01:49.526 --> 00:01:51.611
