33
00:01:51.695 --> 00:01:53.196
Yes.

34
00:01:55.032 --> 00:01:57.450
l'm not sure
we can trust him.
Can he get me inside or not?

35
00:01:57.534 --> 00:01:58.868
Ηe says he can.

36
00:01:58.952 --> 00:02:00.870
