60
00:03:02.683 --> 00:03:05.726
[ Whispering, lndistinct ]

61
00:03:05.811 --> 00:03:07.186
[ Gasps ]

62
00:03:07.271 --> 00:03:08.729
My family!

63
00:03:08.814 --> 00:03:12.233
My family!
You promised
to protect them!

64
00:03:17.990 --> 00:03:20.449
