68
00:03:25.455 --> 00:03:28.791
So why don't you
get your phones ready
and give us a call?

69
00:03:28.876 --> 00:03:32.128
They say that Washingtonians
are apathetic, and l don't
find that to be the case.

70
00:03:32.212 --> 00:03:34.964
