Sergeant Brody?

119
00:07:25.529 --> 00:07:27.655
l realize
it sounds like a reach.

120
00:07:27.739 --> 00:07:29.824
To say the least.

121
00:07:29.908 --> 00:07:32.618
Why not just drop him near
a checkpoint, make it look
like he escaped?

122
00:07:32.702 --> 00:07:34.954
