202
00:12:14.150 --> 00:12:16.485
Come here, you two.

203
00:12:20.323 --> 00:12:22.241
[ Cabin Bell Dings ]

204
00:12:29.833 --> 00:12:32.918
[ Man ] Τouchdown
in about two hours.
