Sergeant Brody was operating
in hostile territory...

219
00:13:20.049 --> 00:13:21.383
when his spotter-

220
00:13:21.468 --> 00:13:22.968
Hi, Brody.

221
00:13:23.052 --> 00:13:24.553
The soldiers
were then separated-

222
00:13:26.973 --> 00:13:29.683
