224
00:13:32.353 --> 00:13:35.314
Yeah. Let me
just get my coat.

225
00:13:35.398 --> 00:13:38.233
Are you really
wearing that dress?

226
00:13:38.318 --> 00:13:40.944
The announcement
that Sergeant Brody, in fact,

227
00:13:41.029 --> 00:13:42.988
